snippet.title: TripTrap Android Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
TripTrap is now available on Google Play and is free!
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.duellogames.TripTrap_Android

TripTrap is a tasty new puzzler from the creators of iSlash! 
In this unique puzzle you help our little hungry mouse Ched to flip and flop his way through dangerous paths and get the cheese avoiding the traps!

Also available on iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/app/triptrap/id712124936
